Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari, where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:26.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You promised you'd be\Nquiet at home for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I know I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:30.55,Main,,0,0,0,,How's your summer homework going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm working on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I just have my reading essay\Nand free research assignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,and half of my English and\NJapanese work, and my art poster left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But I still have lots of summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:50.61,Main,,0,0,0,,And I really am worried about Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:54.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's fine. He seemed entirely well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But that was him from three years ago,\Nand he hasn't been back since!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What if something happened\Nto him in the world of the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:05.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Even so, that's no reason for you\Nto throw yourself into danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you're not going to do anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll worry about Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,So no more dangerous--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:23.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:24.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:30.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari, watch the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.35,Main,,0,0,0,,"Episode 10\NHertz's Pride"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I searched around like you asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:42.82,Main,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't find anything that\Nlooked like the matter transporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't we ask someone directly involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:04:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you people doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for calling her\Nwithout asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You do work fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mikage, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,We just came here to retrieve that\Nwhich our company's funds have paid for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You know where it is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,English done. Japanese done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Essay done. Free research project done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Art poster done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.39,Main,,0,0,0,,All homework done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Waka, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.44,Main,,0,0,0,,D'oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,H-How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you wouldn't answer your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I turned it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:19.71,Main,,0,0,0,,So this was the only way I could\Nget here without your mom seeing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:24.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell Mama I was coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm really worried about Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.39,Main,,0,0,0,,That's no reason to come without asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You only just got out of a really\Ndangerous situation, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I was really scared, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Shun? Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.98,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:45.28,Main,,0,0,0,,But Papa might be going through\Nthe same thing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:50.66,Main,,0,0,0,,If Papa wants to come back and can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:54.41,Main,,0,0,0,,then I want to save him like Shun saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.71,Main,,0,0,0,,So first, I have to find the Papa\Nfrom three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.63,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Waka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Lend me that book!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:11.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Waka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:20.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? It was just right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,My brother always hides\Nhis important stuff here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Heinrich Hertz?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, the EM guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,EM?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Waka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:50.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Waka, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... it sure is windy today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:20.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Waka... Did something happen\Nto Mr. Hayase's laboratory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a policeman there\Nforbidding anyone to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Year 1893\N(What is now) Bonn, Germany"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.73,Main,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:45.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I wasn't in the water this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,But where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:56.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! There's a lot you want to ask, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,But just wait a minute.\NLet me put on my shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,...Dr. Hayase's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,But you're older than I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.15,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, the color...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall I turn on the transmitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I will proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:49.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Getting to see the famous electromagnetic\Nwave experiment with my own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Hertz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, it's just a proof of concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:09:01.10,Main,,0,0,0,,And lately, I've been more focused\Non cathode ray experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Cathode rays?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hertz, you should cut back\Non those experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:13.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you to stop them entirely,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.74,Main,,0,0,0,,but just conduct fewer of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.74,Main,,0,0,0,,or keep your distance\Nfrom the cathode rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:24.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just, the effect\Ncathode rays have on the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Their effect on the body?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lenard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,He warned me that day, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So Papa is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, he came twice to my laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.98,Main,,0,0,0,,But what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm searching for Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Searching?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:53.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know where he might have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hayase, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:00.70,Main,,0,0,0,,If he's anywhere,\Nit might be the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.28,Main,,0,0,0,,University?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Bonn University, where I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,He's always...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine... Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Johanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It might fix your cough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.11,Main,,0,0,0,,The daughter of a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Johanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Reading is all well and good,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.25,Main,,0,0,0,,but it's time to get ready\Nto leave the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not going to go home\Nin your robe, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:58.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Good point. I'll get ready right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, Elisabeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Could we stop by the university\Nbefore we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.72,Main,,0,0,0,,This girl is looking for her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.65,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a policeman at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That's awful... Where's Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.28,Main,,0,0,0,,She's in the past right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,The past? What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.83,Main,,0,0,0,,She was in so much danger last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,B-But she was really worried\Nabout her father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The fact that she was in danger before\Nmade her want to help him even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, wait until I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Waka? What's wrong? Waka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Professor! You're out of the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was just discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, has Dr. Hayase been in recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... he was here this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? S-So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the doctor's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:24.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you were off today,\Nhe said he'd visit you at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:29.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's wait for him at my house then, Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Johanna here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. You should find Johanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,But the university is so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.60,Main,,0,0,0,,It might fix your cough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:13.56,Main,,0,0,0,,The plant diagrams...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.31,Main,,0,0,0,,The garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,There is a botanical garden\Non the grounds. Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Johanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know how worried we were about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:51.05,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,\Nyou can't just run off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make Papa feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:16.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No! I wanna stir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:25.67,Main,,0,0,0,,The cake's done! Mathilde, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.35,Main,,0,0,0,,This should be very easy for Papa to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Mathilde...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:42.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you put the fruit topping on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Smells so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I need to prepare\Nthe herbal tea, and we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What kind of herbal tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Chamomile and marigold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I hear it's good for a cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.25,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You need to put them on\Nmore neatly! It's all messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:07.13,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,--No! I'm doing it!\N--Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:17.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa, I helped with the cake and the soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud, Johanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:23.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I made the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:26.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm proud of you too, Mathilde.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I made this soup with the\NPlantago asiatica Johanna found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa, eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just delicious, Johanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it truly is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You two eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm full, so I think I'll go lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll have more soup tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I need to lay out Papa's robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Eat up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Darling...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't apologize. You haven't\Ndone anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this is what I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:36.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Heinrich, I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Elisabeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:47.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But my research... what good will it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa! I'm so glad! I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something I wanted\Nto let Mr. Hertz know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to talk to my husband, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:20.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll let my husband know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,So would you please wait a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,After we parted ways at Mr. Bell's place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,the armillary compass malfunctioned,\Nand I almost didn't get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,So I thought the same thing might have\Nhappened to you, and you can't get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey... After we get back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.92,Main,,0,0,0,,would you promise not to time travel again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:49.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama's really worried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.75,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad! Then let's go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:01.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari, do you know what Mr. Hertz discovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Electromagnetic waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,The electromagnetic wave experiments he did
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,will later lead to the invention\Nof wireless broadcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:16.99,Main,,0,0,0,,But he dies without ever knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.03,Main,,0,0,0,,the value of his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to let him know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Let him know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to use this to show him\Nthe wonders of wireless transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:32.17,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, the wonders\Nof what he created.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,But won't that change history?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It won't change history.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to let him know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.51,Main,,0,0,0,,And he's not long for this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,His research is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I want him to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But my research... what good will it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You're from the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:19.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you won't believe me right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:23.93,Main,,0,0,0,,but I feel like it's faster\Nto show you than to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Could I take a photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,A photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on, smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.11,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a good photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get too shocked just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.04,Main,,0,0,0,,The real show is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to send this photo\Nto the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Send it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm using wireless transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Wireless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But you can see the picture I\Njust took in the next room over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,The picture he took was sent to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.69,Main,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,The electromagnetic waves\Nsent it from that room to this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,This is something that\Nyour research created.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Electromagnetic waves...\NMy research did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Won't you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,We believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,So you should believe in\Nyour work too, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Believe in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:09.08,Main,,0,0,0,,My research... It's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Elisabeth, Johanna, Mathilde... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:25.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari, I can't go back with you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:29.47,Main,,0,0,0,,But I promise I will return to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So believe and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, go on ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I'll return, too. Goodbye, Mr. Hertz.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:17.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome back from\Nthe other side of space-time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:22.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:27.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mama's out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:28.15,Main,,0,0,0,,"Next Episode: Edison's Resilience"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:29.74,Main,,0,0,0,,She's late.\N"Next Episode: Edison's Resilience"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:29.99,Main,,0,0,0,,"Next Episode: Edison's Resilience"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:00.79,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mari and Waka's Quick Science"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.79,0:24:03.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari and Waka's Quick Science!\N"Mari and Waka's Quick Science"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:04.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari and Waka's Quick Science!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I will proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:16.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Getting to see the famous electromagnetic\Nwave experiment with my own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:20.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, it's just a proof of concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What was Mr. Hertz's experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.77,0:24:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,He was proving the existence\Nof electromagnetic waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.94,0:24:29.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Electromagnetic waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.57,0:24:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Waves created by electricity\Nand magnetism, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.36,0:24:34.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,He theorized their existence based on the\Nequation of a physicist named Maxwell,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.08,0:24:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,and proved that electromagnetic waves\Nmove through space and expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.46,0:24:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Through space?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.58,0:24:50.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Electromagnetic waves are generated\Nwhen electricity is flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.76,0:24:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Then every other experiment before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.38,0:24:56.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, they produced\Nelectromagnetic waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.34,0:24:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,People just didn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.30,0:24:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.35,0:24:59.81,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Types of Electromagnetic Waves"\N"Radio Waves"\N"Light" "X-Rays/Gamma Rays"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.81,0:25:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Depending on their wavelength,\Nelectromagnetic waves\N"The Types of Electromagnetic Waves"\N"Radio Waves"\N"Light" "X-Rays/Gamma Rays"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.85,0:25:07.65,Main,,0,0,0,,can be radio waves, light,\Nor X-rays or gamma rays.\N"The Types of Electromagnetic Waves"\N"Radio Waves"\N"Light" "X-Rays/Gamma Rays"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.65,0:25:10.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, light is an electromagnetic wave, too?\N"The Types of Electromagnetic Waves"\N"Radio Waves"\N"Light" "X-Rays/Gamma Rays"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.82,0:25:11.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!\N"The Types of Electromagnetic Waves"\N"Radio Waves"\N"Light" "X-Rays/Gamma Rays"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.73,0:25:14.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Light is just electromagnetic waves\Non the visible spectrum!\N"The Types of Electromagnetic Waves"\N"Radio Waves"\N"Light" "X-Rays/Gamma Rays"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.03,0:25:17.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Electromagnetic waves are\Nused in TV and cell phones,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.87,0:25:21.87,Main,,0,0,0,,and X-rays are used for\Nmany medical procedures.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.87,0:25:23.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.45,0:25:28.71,Main,,0,0,0,,And what are they measured in,\Nas credit for the great accomplishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.71,0:25:30.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Hertz!\N"Hertz"
